<hgroup><h1>Angiotensin receptor blockers: are they related to lung cancer?</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Rao%20GA"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Gowtham Adamane Rao</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
